Package model

Class NodeName

java.lang.Object
model.NodeName
public class NodeName extends Object
Represents a node in a singly linked list of names for the phone book structure. Each node contains a name, phone number, and a reference to the next name node in the alphabetical sequence.

This node is part of the NameList structure that organizes names alphabetically within each letter group in the phone book.

Since:
2024
